@startuml Authentication Sequence

participant User
participant System
participant Database

User -> System: Enter Credentials
System -> System: Validate Input
System -> System: Hash Password
System -> Database: Check User Exists
Database --> System: User Data
System -> Database: Verify Password Hash
Database --> System: Password Valid

alt Valid Credentials
    System -> System: Create Session
    System -> System: Set Role (Student/Admin)
    
    alt Role = Admin
        System --> User: Route to Admin Dashboard
    else Role = Student
        System --> User: Redirect to Student Portal
    end
    
else Invalid Credentials
    System --> User: Show Login Error
end

@enduml